# Reports are not committed to Git at all. Each report notebook (docs/**/*.py) is the
# source of truth; `./go publish` exports it to a self-contained bundle (index.html +
# named-keyed _assets/) and mirrors that to the HF bucket under exports/<key>/. The
# Pages build pulls the synced bundles and assembles the site. No exported HTML, no
# heavy assets, and no Git LFS in the repo.
